Instructions to run the program:
 1. Set up a local Python environment with Python 3.7.5.
 2. Copy all the files from the GitHub directory into your Python environment.
 3. Install all the packages in the requirements.txt file using “pip install -r requirements.txt”.
 4. Insert your Spoonacular API key in line 16 in the file RecipeFinder_Chatbot.py
 5. Run RecipeFinder_Chatbot.py
 6. Ignore the error messages. They appear because some packages don’t support the newest tensorflow package yet.
 7. Find your favorite recipe and enjoy the food!
